import {Typography} from '@material-ui/core';

const Home = () => {
    return(
        <>
        <Typography>Jambo, I am Erick Lumunge</Typography>
        <Typography>
            The internet is the greatest reward to mankind as it offers us a wide range of
             choices and opportunities in contrast to outdated conventional ways where a group controlled what we know or do. This is my inspiration
              to being a developer because i can build anything i want. Software the makes an impact in peoples lives from a simple blog the shares 
              awesome stories to inspire people in the morining as they get to work to an ecommerce website that allows people to shop at the conveniece 
              of their homes to health systems that advices users on their health status for free imporoving the quality of life of people the search engines
              that save us years of college to social media that connects people.
             Life was meant to be easy and the internet has proved that.
             Conventional eductaion did not serve me as i expected, I failed terribly in school in topic like history, biology, chemistry and this 
             impacted my view on life but this all changed when i joined college and pursued what i liked, Computer Science. I started excelling to the point
             where i discovered that doing what you love makes success a joke and life a game so i have been playing ever since back in 2018. I dived
             into deeper computer science topics which intoduced me to code, the primary factor that all technolgy is built upon and l loved code ever since.
             </Typography>
        </>
    )
}

export default Home;
